channel.title: CreativeScape [Anti-Leech removed, fixed]
channel.description:
[size=14pt][b]If anyone wants me to remove this, please say so and I will.[/b][/size]
Since people have been asking me how to fix the CreativeScape client, how to fix the commands, etc, I thought I would post this with the fixes. [b]Also, please note:[/b] I don't care if you think it was easy to fix; it was. This is for the people who couldn't fix it.
[size=12pt][b]CREDITS: 99.9% to original creator .1% to me for removing the anti-leech, fixing the client, and fixing some server things. (Like, 1 or 2 things.)[/b][/size]
[size=12pt][b]For the original topic with the features etc, click [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,440915.msg3239114.html#msg3239114]here[/url].[/b][/size]
[b]FAQs:[/b] How can I spawn? Go into [b]server - model - player - command - Itemspawn.java[/b] Change [code]Evo[/code] to your username.
Commands? Go into CommandManager.java and look.
How do I make myself admin? Make yourself the owner by yourself. If you can't; you don't deserve this. Go into [b]config - rights - admin.conf[/b] Then add your name inside.
